<head>ACTOR</head>
    <list type="translations">
        <item xml:lang="zh">演員</item>
    </list>
<div type="definition">
<p>An ENTERTAINER who DISPLAYS ACTS in DRAMAS.</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
